# Solicitation Review Report — 36C26126Q0064

---

## I. Solicitation Overview

**Title/Number:** S203--CLC Long-Term Food Service (36C26126Q0064)  
**Agency:** Department of Veterans Affairs, Network Contracting Office 21 (NCO 21)  
**Type:** RFQ, Small Business Set Aside  
**NAICS:** 624210 (Size Standard: $19.5M)

---

## II. Scope of Work

- **Requirements:** Provide all labor, equipment, materials, and supervision to prepare, serve, and clean up three daily meals (including dietary accommodations) for residents at:
  - Community Living Center (CLC)
  - Psychosocial Residential Rehabilitation Program (PRRP)
- **Population:** High Sensitivity/At-Risk (long-term care, skilled nursing, rehabilitation, psychosocial—may have dietary restrictions/allergies).
- **Location:** Tripler Army Medical Center, 110 Krukowski Road, Building 110, Honolulu, HI 96819.
- **Other Services:** Stock resident-purchase vending machines, provide disposables for emergencies only.

